<i>adverb</i>: 본시 [본시], 본래 [볼래], 본디 [본디] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>본시 [본시]</dt><br>
<dd>originally</dd><br>
<dd>맨 처음부터. 또는 근본부터.</dd><br>
<dd>From the beginning; by nature.</dd><br>
<dt>본래 [볼래]</dt><br>
<dd>originally</dd><br>
